Id":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","characterAId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","characterBId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000009","label":"Close Friends","strength":"strong","sentiment":"positive","description":"Wilem provides steady, level-headed friendship and academic camaraderie.","isBidirectional":true,"startEventId":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"type":"friendship"},{"id":"73311964-968e-4cd7-9055-6e4c731fb67c","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","characterAId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","characterBId":"b1e30133-29d0-4f94-8f70-e33df9d9f312","label":"Debtor & Lender","strength":"weak","sentiment":"complex","description":"Devi loans Kvothe money when he is desperate, holding his blood in a vial as collateral. Their relationship is wary mutual respect.","isBidirectional":false,"startEventId":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"type":"business"},{"id":"75912610-3b3b-4e9b-a9f4-f34518cc9601","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","characterAId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","characterBId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","label":"Narrator & Subject","type":"professional","strength":"moderate","sentiment":"complex","startEventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"a43d26fc-609a-4798-abfc-a18faaa59ed1","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","characterAId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","characterBId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000019","label":"Hunter & Prey","type":"nemesis","strength":"strong","sentiment":"negative","startEventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000016","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"b62d2d0d-3cd0-474c-bb6b-cd3ae82132bb","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","characterAId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","characterBId":"de769a56-8aa4-4235-9a5c-fb52cf75bef7","label":"Student & Antagonist","strength":"moderate","sentiment":"negative","description":"Hemme openly dislikes Kvothe and attempts to have him punished. Kvothe humiliates Hemme in his own class using sympathy, deepening the enmity.","isBidirectional":true,"startEventId":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"type":"rivals"},{"id":"d1f6e409-ebb2-4d66-98cf-c88de5d21d42","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","characterAId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000008","characterBId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000009","label":"Best Friends","type":"friendship","strength":"bond","sentiment":"positive","startEventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"ef0b6c7b-c07b-4510-9da7-8ff9a5f347b4","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","characterAId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","characterBId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006","label":"First Teacher","type":"mentor","strength":"strong","sentiment":"positive","startEventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000008","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000}],"relationshipSnapshots":[{"id":"05df131a-c48e-4ff4-9b02-2de6fe451b02","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"2701478e-099a-4d2b-aff3-3bd1424c0b35","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000067","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Genuine Esteem","description":"Kvothe's bravery in the Fishery fire raises his standing with Kilvin enormously.","sortKey":67.000067,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"155643ca-9036-42af-aa21-b1a0546aba4a","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"38e961e4-cb6a-4f86-8f96-d1c4bf84dc23","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000016","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"bond","label":"Mother & Son (Grief)","description":"Laurian is dead. Her loss is as devastating as Arliden's — the family that made Kvothe whole is gone.","sortKey":16.000016,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"1624cd54-fd9f-496a-8b97-5b446d79b305","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"bond","label":"Master & Student","description":"As Kvothe begins his story, Bast is both audience and custodian — hoping the act of telling will somehow restore his master.","sortKey":6.000006,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"1a89e3f4-c6de-4bce-bac8-94fe92e02510","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000043","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Steady Support","description":"When Ambrose destroys Kvothe's lute, Simmon is there — quietly offering comfort and solidarity.","sortKey":43.000043,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"22ed8b4a-b815-46b8-ac99-32681bf3d9cd","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"4a0c789b-2642-4aa3-a8fb-0498f13ce58d","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000016","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"strong","label":"Fear and Obsession","description":"Haliax commanded Cinder to leave Kvothe alive. Whether mercy or cruelty, Kvothe cannot say. He will find the Chandrian.","sortKey":16.000016,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"23e3bcfd-92b1-45e7-953c-7ccd75c0dfad","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000064","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Enduring Companion","description":"Through financial ruin and University politics, Simmon remains Kvothe's most uncomplicated ally.","sortKey":64.000064,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"25cbcdad-2a42-4a80-a2ad-4f330c458f1d","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"75912610-3b3b-4e9b-a9f4-f34518cc9601","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"weak","label":"Wary Subject","description":"Kvothe is reluctant; Chronicler has tracked him down and wants the truth. Kvothe agrees to talk, on his own terms.","sortKey":5.000005,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"2fd4be83-15f6-4bfc-ad60-5c33ce09dcd1","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"d1f6e409-ebb2-4d66-98cf-c88de5d21d42","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"bond","label":"Best Friends","description":"Simmon and Wilem have been close friends at the University long before Kvothe arrives.","sortKey":31.000031,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"32aef0b1-8df1-4082-a8c1-1b4208ae54a0","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"27e80be0-9665-4377-acbc-b71f817b0e48","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000016","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"bond","label":"Father & Son (Grief)","description":"Arliden is dead. Kvothe is left with a hollow, shattering grief and a burning need to understand why.","sortKey":16.000016,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"3f72f9fc-6793-490f-b1f5-12c5565abfc2","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000032","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"True Friendship","description":"After initial awkwardness, Simmon and Kvothe fall into a comfortable and loyal friendship over shared meals and conversation.","sortKey":32.000032,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"435ae64e-5164-461b-9dd5-c5e16873957b","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000056","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"strong","label":"Crisis and Care","description":"Kvothe finds Denna drugged near Trebon. His fear for her safety makes plain the depth of his feelings.","sortKey":56.000056,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"4fee499a-b5bf-4082-b823-4d692a22eec8","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"2701478e-099a-4d2b-aff3-3bd1424c0b35","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"Promising Student","description":"Kilvin notices Kvothe's potential at admissions. He offers a path in the Fishery almost immediately.","sortKey":31.000031,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"50c16cc0-1dd5-427a-9d36-faad2546b76c","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"75912610-3b3b-4e9b-a9f4-f34518cc9601","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"moderate","label":"Narrator & Recorder","description":"The agreement is struck: three days, three books, the unvarnished truth. Kvothe controls the story; Chronicler writes it.","sortKey":6.000006,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"52d3349e-b44d-493b-8cd8-6016cebc46b6","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"d1f6e409-ebb2-4d66-98cf-c88de5d21d42","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000053","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"bond","label":"Inseparable","description":"Where Simmon goes, Wilem tends to follow — and vice versa. Their friendship is one of the most solid things at the University.","sortKey":53.000053,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"59986e42-27a8-47f0-ad76-7d3489e9390e","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000044","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"strong","label":"Retribution","description":"Kvothe retaliates, making Ambrose appear foolish. Neither will back down.","sortKey":44.000044,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"6267bf68-31b9-4bf5-9584-f9cb1b2d6fe1","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000041","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"Growing Infatuation","description":"Kvothe sees Denna again at the Eolian in Imre. She cheers for him; the connection deepens, though it remains painfully unspoken.","sortKey":41.000041,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"6885a6d6-f7ac-400f-b131-1d8a5127232f","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000041","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Trusted Friend","description":"Wilem is a steady presence at the Eolian. He does not flatter Kvothe, and that makes his praise mean more.","sortKey":41.000041,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"68bc322a-af65-4d53-bf68-048dc86557fc","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"38e961e4-cb6a-4f86-8f96-d1c4bf84dc23","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"bond","label":"Mother & Son","description":"Laurian is warm, sharp-tongued, and deeply loving — she teaches Kvothe the value of words and memory.","sortKey":7.000007,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"70f9fa04-5f34-4ddd-b8f1-b0e8a0610e2d","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"27e80be0-9665-4377-acbc-b71f817b0e48","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"bond","label":"Father & Son","description":"Kvothe idolises his father — a gifted musician and storyteller who shapes everything about how Kvothe sees the world.","sortKey":7.000007,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"820414b1-2e8f-4182-adc5-b2efa787b636","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"New Friend","description":"Simmon is one of the first people to welcome Kvothe at the University with genuine warmth.","sortKey":31.000031,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"85247912-e76f-4cbb-9868-79aa9589abb9","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"bond","label":"Master & Student","description":"Bast serves Kvothe at the Waystone Inn with complete loyalty, though he quietly grieves the diminished man his master has become.","sortKey":0,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"8fcece5a-dbf6-42db-b4d0-47fec96de9ef","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"Cautious Respect","description":"Wilem is guarded at first, but Kvothe's ability earns his genuine respect quickly.","sortKey":31.000031,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"90000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000028","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"Acquaintance / Spark","description":"Kvothe and Denna meet on the road and feel an immediate, profound spark.","sortKey":28.000028,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"90000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000035","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"strong","label":"Rivalry Begins","description":"Kvothe meets Ambrose at the Archives, sparking their mutual hatred.","sortKey":35.000035,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"90000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000043","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"bond","label":"Bitter Enemies","description":"The lute destruction turns their rivalry into an open, dangerous war.","sortKey":43.000043,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"9200d08c-2000-4cd6-8714-243a4fb6f9b9","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"b62d2d0d-3cd0-474c-bb6b-cd3ae82132bb","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000039","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"strong","label":"Public Humiliation","description":"Hemme tries to make an example of Kvothe; Kvothe turns it around on him. Hemme is livid.","sortKey":39.000039,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"9496a5d9-57f1-44e4-b63f-2dc8ffc77c1d","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000069","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"strong","label":"Repeated Longing","description":"Time in Imre with Denna is sweet but unsatisfying — the subject of her patron poisons their ease together.","sortKey":69.000069,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"9922197d-a934-4dbc-a402-8a3583f2f00b","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000072","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"bond","label":"Dangerous Enemy","description":"Ambrose's scheming is no longer just petty — he uses his family's influence to put Kvothe at real risk.","sortKey":72.000072,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"9b60fb7a-f8fe-4308-b72f-b6a84aa6065f","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"73311964-968e-4cd7-9055-6e4c731fb67c","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000076","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"moderate","label":"Grudging Respect","description":"Despite the tension, there is a thread of genuine respect between them — two unusually capable people recognising each other.","sortKey":76.000076,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"9b6ae8dc-e613-4d5e-b85b-b26ae40e87a1","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"2701478e-099a-4d2b-aff3-3bd1424c0b35","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000037","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Respected Craftsman","description":"Kilvin respects Kvothe's craftsmanship and ingenuity in the Fishery. The respect is mutual.","sortKey":37.000037,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"a3d3a8d6-12e0-4bee-8eba-248b04021f28","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"b62d2d0d-3cd0-474c-bb6b-cd3ae82132bb","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000034","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"moderate","label":"Mutual Contempt","description":"Hemme singles Kvothe out in his first sympathy class and Kvothe refuses to be cowed — the hostility is immediate.","sortKey":34.000034,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"a431003c-2611-40df-a91c-c0e987e48c6e","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"ef0b6c7b-c07b-4510-9da7-8ff9a5f347b4","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000015","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Parting Ways","description":"Ben departs from the troupe. Kvothe is sad but grateful — the foundation Ben laid will shape everything that follows.","sortKey":15.000015,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"aa397018-e7c1-481a-ade6-562b938525b7","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"a43d26fc-609a-4798-abfc-a18faaa59ed1","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000016","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"strong","label":"The Killer","description":"Cinder is the face of everything Kvothe has lost. He taunted the boy over the bodies of his family.","sortKey":16.000016,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"aa84b5bc-09ac-4fc4-86ab-3f0b109a9154","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"73311964-968e-4cd7-9055-6e4c731fb67c","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000046","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"weak","label":"Cautious Transaction","description":"Devi lends Kvothe money with cold professionalism. She takes his blood and makes clear what it means.","sortKey":46.000046,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"ae3e2085-93f7-47ad-aeb2-407220627582","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"074ea5cb-85f8-4ffa-aaa9-602944fefcc5","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000082","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"Strange Progress","description":"Elodin's teaching is maddening but Kvothe begins to suspect there is a method beneath the apparent chaos.","sortKey":82.000082,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"af78cd39-8fbc-4ef0-91f6-e45fcb5ef68f","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000084","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"strong","label":"Growing Strain","description":"Kvothe's suspicion about Master Ash creates friction. Their connection is as real as ever, and as frustrated.","sortKey":84.000084,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"b8cb6500-6a97-4ac9-a7ed-b8e59c0043a3","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000032","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Real Friendship","description":"Wilem and Kvothe settle into a friendship built on honesty and mutual regard, without pretense.","sortKey":32.000032,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"bf8ddd9a-5d3d-4635-a463-12f662591d77","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000053","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Fellow Adventurer","description":"Simmon travels to Trebon with Kvothe despite the risk. His loyalty is never in question.","sortKey":53.000053,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"c686aedd-c722-40fb-86fc-f10253d04e54","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"b62d2d0d-3cd0-474c-bb6b-cd3ae82132bb","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000040","isActive":true,"sentiment":"negative","strength":"strong","label":"Formal Punishment","description":"Hemme takes Kvothe before the masters. The proceedings (\"On the Horns\") nearly end Kvothe's University career.","sortKey":40.00004,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"cac9587d-0167-4e50-9dc2-c2b873554795","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"ef0b6c7b-c07b-4510-9da7-8ff9a5f347b4","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000008","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"Curious Student","description":"Kvothe pesters Ben with questions about sympathy, astonishing him with how quickly he grasps the fundamentals.","sortKey":8.000008,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"cc75ece6-a0ea-4267-8d0d-7d54840b9ac8","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000042","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"moderate","label":"Uncertain Feeling","description":"They spend time together in Imre, talking and playing music, but Denna keeps her secrets and Kvothe keeps his pride.","sortKey":42.000042,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"d222dacc-204d-49b1-84b5-28a02b14f21c","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"73311964-968e-4cd7-9055-6e4c731fb67c","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000064","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"moderate","label":"Power Imbalance","description":"Devi holds significant power over Kvothe via his blood. Their relationship is a careful dance of mutual wariness.","sortKey":64.000064,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"d6020091-6af4-4f7a-969d-d697d0b2f4dd","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"27e80be0-9665-4377-acbc-b71f817b0e48","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000015","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"bond","label":"Father & Son","description":"The troupe is close-knit. Kvothe and Arliden share musical evenings and long conversations on the road.","sortKey":15.000015,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"d960abc9-cbd4-43d3-995e-16bce0ac01df","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"074ea5cb-85f8-4ffa-aaa9-602944fefcc5","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000068","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"Reluctant Teacher","description":"Elodin agrees to teach Kvothe Naming after being worn down. He is nothing like any other instructor Kvothe has had.","sortKey":68.000068,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"e0a77d16-9d83-4956-a093-550e4242382e","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000092","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"bond","label":"Keeper of the Legend","description":"One day of the story told. Bast watches over Kvothe with fierce devotion, frustrated by his master's resignation.","sortKey":92.000092,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"e5f3add5-06f7-43e0-8fae-da67a662a27d","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"ef0b6c7b-c07b-4510-9da7-8ff9a5f347b4","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000014","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Teacher & Prodigy","description":"Ben has pushed Kvothe further than any student he has known. Their bond has deepened into true friendship.","sortKey":14.000014,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"eba46306-1589-4959-b8c7-1885f7e52d14","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"75912610-3b3b-4e9b-a9f4-f34518cc9601","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000092","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"moderate","label":"Growing Trust","description":"The first day's account is complete. Chronicler is shaken by the distance between legend and man.","sortKey":92.000092,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"f51bab64-ff89-45b4-8a04-f1226459217e","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"074ea5cb-85f8-4ffa-aaa9-602944fefcc5","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"weak","label":"Inscrutable Master","description":"Elodin's response to Kvothe at admissions is strange and unreadable — as if he's testing something else entirely.","sortKey":31.000031,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"f73af501-6b69-47d5-905d-f237a4df1145","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"50000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000062","isActive":true,"sentiment":"complex","strength":"strong","label":"Parting Again","description":"They recover together but Denna leaves before anything can be resolved. She always slips away.","sortKey":62.000062,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"fdfa59cb-0a40-405e-9d8b-88462d25ef85","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","relationshipId":"ef0b6c7b-c07b-4510-9da7-8ff9a5f347b4","eventId":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000009","isActive":true,"sentiment":"positive","strength":"strong","label":"Eager Apprentice","description":"Ben formally teaches Kvothe sympathy, recognising his exceptional ability and taking genuine delight in it.","sortKey":9.000009,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000}],"timelines":[{"id":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","name":"The Waystone","description":"The framing present narrative at the Waystone Inn.","color":"#6366f1","createdAt":1713200000000},{"id":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","name":"Kvothe's Story","description":"The inner narrative recounting Kvothe's childhood and time at the University.","color":"#f59e0b","createdAt":1713200000000}],"chapters":[{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":0,"title":"Prologue: A Silence of Three Parts","synopsis":"A detailed, layered description of the three silences that fill the Waystone Inn — the silence of a man who has given up, set against the ordinary sounds of an inn at rest.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":1,"title":"A Place for Demons","synopsis":"Scraels are found near Newarre. Old Cob's stories run to demons; Kote and Bast deal with the creature practically. The locals are frightened of the spreading darkness on the roads.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":2,"title":"A Beautiful Day","synopsis":"A quiet day at the inn. Kote is performing the role of innkeeper with the exhausting thoroughness of someone who has rehearsed it until the performance becomes indistinguishable from the person.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":3,"title":"Wood and Word","synopsis":"Jake Carter is found injured by a scrael. The locals gather; the talk is of safety, the roads, and the strangeness creeping into familiar things.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":4,"title":"Blood, Ink, and Dapple","synopsis":"Chronicler arrives and is saved from a scrael attack. Kote tends his wounds. Bast recognises who Chronicler is before Kote does, and something shifts in the inn's equilibrium.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":5,"title":"Notes","synopsis":"Chronicler reveals his purpose: he wants to record Kvothe's life in full. Kvothe deflects, offers the comfortable legend, and is finally worn down into agreeing to the truth.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":6,"title":"The Price of Remembering","synopsis":"Kvothe sets his terms and begins. The first words of the real story.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":7,"title":"Of Beginnings and the Names of Things","synopsis":"The life of the Edema Ruh: roads and fire, music and story, the close world of the troupe. Kvothe at seven, ten, twelve — happy and ignorant and full of questions.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000008","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":8,"title":"Thieves, Heretics, and Whores","synopsis":"Ben joins the troupe and Kvothe immediately begins to study him. The first sympathy demonstration. The beginning of a real education.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000009","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":9,"title":"Riding in the Wagon with Ben","synopsis":"Ben teaches Kvothe formally. The Alar. The disciplines. The costs. Kvothe's aptitude is extraordinary and Ben is not sure whether to be proud or worried.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000010","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":10,"title":"Alar and Several Stones","synopsis":"Kvothe works on the split-mind technique until it becomes effortless — or near enough. Ben tests him with coins and candles and progressively stranger tasks.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":11,"title":"The Binding of Iron","synopsis":"The first real binding — heat drawn from one thing and sent to another. Kvothe feels the sympathist's price: what you take has to come from somewhere. He grins.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":12,"title":"Puzzle Pieces Fit","synopsis":"Kvothe's research into the Chandrian from Ben's books. Ben is careful about what he confirms and what he leaves unsaid.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":13,"title":"Interlude: Flesh with Blood Beneath","synopsis":"The first frame narrative pause. Kvothe and Chronicler and Bast rest in the inn. The story breathes.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000014","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":14,"title":"The Name of the Wind","synopsis":"Ben teaches Kvothe to call the wind by name — not sympathy, something older. The lesson frightens Ben more than it frightens his student.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000015","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":15,"title":"Distractions and Farewells","synopsis":"Ben leaves the troupe. Fond farewells, practical advice, a shadow of foreboding. He urges Kvothe toward the University and away from the Chandrian.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000016","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":16,"title":"Hope Falling","synopsis":"Kvothe returns to the camp to find everyone dead. The fire, the bodies, the terrible stillness. His parents are among them. He catches one glimpse of Cinder before shock takes him.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000017","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":17,"title":"Interlude: Derian","synopsis":"Frame pause. Kvothe's voice is flat. He is not performing grief; he is simply reporting what was there.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000018","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":18,"title":"Roads to Safe Places","synopsis":"Kvothe wanders, lost in shock. Weeks of empty roads and no purpose. The lute is somewhere in his arms but he barely plays.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000019","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":19,"title":"Fingers and Strings","synopsis":"Music finds him again — or he finds it. Playing for hours until his fingers bleed, then more. A stranger offers him a ride to Tarbean.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000020","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":20,"title":"Bloody-Handed Amyr","synopsis":"Tarbean: vast, indifferent, brutal. Kvothe arrives a child and immediately understands that this city will not make any accommodation for him.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000021","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":21,"title":"Black Hands","synopsis":"Three years condensed: Kvothe's life as a street urchin. Begging, thieving, surviving. Calling himself Kote. The person he used to be feels like a story about someone else.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000022","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":22,"title":"A Time for Demons","synopsis":"The Midwinter celebration. Cold, crowded, Kvothe in a holding pen. Religion and ceremony glimpsed from the outside.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000023","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":23,"title":"The Burning Wheel","synopsis":"Skarpi the storyteller tells the real history of Lanre in a Tarbean tavern — a history the church does not want told. Kvothe listens all night.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000024","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":24,"title":"Shadows","synopsis":"Something wakes in Kvothe. He retrieves his lute, patches it badly, and starts playing again. He is going to leave.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000025","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":25,"title":"Defending the Edema Ruh","synopsis":"On the road, Kvothe intervenes when soldiers harass a Ruh family. The old instincts — and the old anger — are intact.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000026","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":26,"title":"Lanre Turned","synopsis":"Skarpi is arrested by a church inquisitor. Kvothe watches. The inquisitor is terrifyingly calm.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000027","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":27,"title":"The Meaning of a Word","synopsis":"Kvothe prepares himself for the University. He reviews what Ben taught him. He plans.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000028","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":28,"title":"Tehlu's Watchful Eye","synopsis":"The road to the University and a brief, unforgettable encounter with a girl named Denna.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000029","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":29,"title":"The Doors of My Mind","synopsis":"Traveling with Denna for a short stretch. Then the paths diverge. Kvothe continues alone toward the University with Denna still turning over in his thoughts.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000030","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":30,"title":"The Loden-Stone","synopsis":"Arrival at the University. The size of it. The rules. The fact that Kvothe has to pass admissions before any of it matters.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":31,"title":"The Crucible","synopsis":"Admissions. Kvothe performs beyond expectation — answering questions in three languages, demonstrating sympathy, impressing nearly everyone. His tuition is set at three talents.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000032","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":32,"title":"The Edge of the Map","synopsis":"The first term begins. Kvothe meets Simmon and Wilem and begins learning the rhythms of the University.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000033","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":33,"title":"A Sea of Stars","synopsis":"The Archives. Kvothe falls in love with the idea of a building full of every book ever written and begins looking for information on the Chandrian immediately.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000034","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":34,"title":"Yet to Learn","synopsis":"Hemme's class. Kvothe navigates the hostile instructor while trying not to do anything that would see him expelled in his first term.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000035","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":35,"title":"Secrets","synopsis":"Ambrose. One conversation and the shape of the rivalry is clear.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000036","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":36,"title":"Less Than Three","synopsis":"Kvothe's bluntness earns him a ban from the Archives. He is devastated.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000037","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":37,"title":"A Piece of Fire","synopsis":"Work in the Fishery begins. Kilvin is a revelation — a master who values skill over politics.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000038","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":38,"title":"Sympathy in the Mains","synopsis":"Kvothe advances through his sympathy studies with embarrassing speed.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000039","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":39,"title":"Hemme's Class","synopsis":"The incident in Hemme's class: sympathy as a weapon, turned around.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000040","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":40,"title":"On the Horns","synopsis":"On the Horns before the masters. Kvothe defends himself and receives a suspended sentence.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000041","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":41,"title":"A Spark in the Ashes","synopsis":"The Eolian. Talent pipes earned.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000042","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":42,"title":"Dust Along the Way","synopsis":"An afternoon in Imre with Denna. Always almost, never quite.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000043","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":43,"title":"The Ass in the Fire","synopsis":"Ambrose destroys Kvothe's lute. The thing Kvothe carried from the Ruh, through Tarbean, all the way here.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000044","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":44,"title":"The Burning Wheel","synopsis":"Revenge. Careful, plausible-deniable, satisfying, and not enough.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000045","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":45,"title":"Interlude: The Innkeeper","synopsis":"Third frame pause. The night is further along. The fire needs feeding.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000046","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":46,"title":"The Ever-Changing Wind","synopsis":"Devi's loan. Blood as collateral. Both parties clear-eyed about what this means.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000047","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":47,"title":"The Bloodless","synopsis":"The Bloodless completed. Re'lar title earned. New lute acquired.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000048","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":48,"title":"Interlude","synopsis":"A term of steady University life — study, work, friendship. The surface of things.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000049","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":49,"title":"The Underthing","synopsis":"The Underthing: hidden passages beneath the University, older than anyone alive remembers.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000050","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":50,"title":"Puppet","synopsis":"Puppet: strange, unsettling, possibly not entirely human. He guards something and seems to know things he shouldn't.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000051","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":51,"title":"Tarbean Again","synopsis":"A brief return to Tarbean in memory and geography. Kvothe does not stop.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000052","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":52,"title":"A Fire In the Blood","synopsis":"Word from Trebon: something terrible happened. Signs of the Chandrian.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000053","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":53,"title":"Slow Circles","synopsis":"The road to Trebon with Simmon.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000054","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":54,"title":"A Place to Burn","synopsis":"Investigation at the destroyed farmstead. Chandrian signs in the wreckage.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000055","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":55,"title":"Blood and Iron","synopsis":"Denna found in the ruins — alive, but drugged with Denner resin.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000056","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":56,"title":"The Draccus","synopsis":"The draccus: a creature the size of a barn, maddened by Denner resin, heading for Trebon.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000057","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":57,"title":"A Piece of the Story","synopsis":"Tracking the draccus toward the village. The difficulty of stopping something with no natural predators.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000058","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":58,"title":"Names for It","synopsis":"Denna comes back to herself. The conversation is difficult.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000059","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":59,"title":"All This Knowing","synopsis":"Kvothe uses sympathy and fire to lead the draccus away from Trebon. The effort costs him nearly everything he has.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000060","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":60,"title":"Blood and Iron (Trebon)","synopsis":"The draccus attacks anyway. Kvothe gets ahead of it. Barely.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000061","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":61,"title":"Ash and Iron","synopsis":"Kvothe destroys the draccus by collapsing the bell tower onto its head. Then lies in the rubble wondering if he is still alive.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000062","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":62,"title":"Leaves","synopsis":"Recovery. Forty talents from the grateful mayor. Denna already gone.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000063","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":63,"title":"The Road to Imre","synopsis":"Return to Imre, exhausted.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000064","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":64,"title":"Less Than a Talent","synopsis":"The forty talents vanish into tuition, debt, and living.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000065","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":65,"title":"Spark","synopsis":"Second term, continued. Sympathy practice and Archives politics.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000066","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":66,"title":"Volatile","synopsis":"The Fishery fire. Fela saved.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000067","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":67,"title":"A Matter of Blood","synopsis":"Aftermath of the fire. The University notices Kvothe in a new way.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000068","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":68,"title":"The Ever-Moving Moon","synopsis":"Elodin agrees to teach Naming. On his own terms, in his own way.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000069","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":69,"title":"Wind or Women's Fancy","synopsis":"Denna in Imre. Beautiful and frustrating and gone.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000070","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":70,"title":"Bones","synopsis":"Advanced sympathy. Multiple simultaneous bindings holding steady.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000071","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":71,"title":"Life and Death","synopsis":"The gram constructed. A small circle of iron with a big purpose.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000072","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":72,"title":"Reactions","synopsis":"Ambrose escalates. Family connections deployed.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000073","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":73,"title":"Blood and Ink","synopsis":"Tuition paid, somehow, again.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000074","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":74,"title":"Rumors","synopsis":"Kvothe's reputation at the University is growing faster than his actual accomplishments.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000075","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":75,"title":"Interlude: Obedience","synopsis":"Fourth frame pause. Kvothe pours more drinks.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000076","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":76,"title":"A Matter of Pride","synopsis":"Back to Devi. More blood-debt negotiations.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000077","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":77,"title":"Bluffs","synopsis":"Kvothe outmanoeuvres one of Ambrose's schemes — and waits for the next.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000078","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":78,"title":"The Master Ash","synopsis":"Master Ash is Denna's patron and Kvothe's growing suspicion. She will not hear it.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000079","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":79,"title":"Secret Things","synopsis":"Archives research: Amyr, Chandrian, ancient wars. Fragments and silences where knowledge should be.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000080","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":80,"title":"A Silence of Three Parts","synopsis":"An ordinary day. Good ones are worth mentioning.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000081","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":81,"title":"Pride","synopsis":"Kvothe's arrogance surfaces in a lesson and he is called on it.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000082","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":82,"title":"Ash and Iron","synopsis":"Elodin: go listen to the wind. Kvothe does. Something at the edge of his mind stirs.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000083","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":83,"title":"Return","synopsis":"Taking stock. The Chandrian are no closer. Denna is no closer. The University continues.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000084","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":84,"title":"A Sudden Storm","synopsis":"The argument in Imre about Master Ash. Things said that cannot be unsaid.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000085","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":85,"title":"Interlude: Familiar","synopsis":"Fifth frame pause. The night has grown very quiet.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000086","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":86,"title":"The Fire Itself","synopsis":"On the road back in a storm, Kvothe names the wind. He knows the name completely and it answers him.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000087","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":87,"title":"Unlikely Things","synopsis":"Back at the University. Sitting with what happened on the road. The world feels different.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000088","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":88,"title":"Interlude: Looking","synopsis":"Sixth frame pause. The story is nearing the end of Day One.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000089","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":89,"title":"A Night in Tarbean","synopsis":"The final stretch of the first day's account.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000090","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":90,"title":"Half-Clever","synopsis":"Kvothe gathers the threads together.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000091","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","number":91,"title":"Worthy of Hiding","synopsis":"The last events of the first day told.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000092","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":92,"title":"The Music that Plays","synopsis":"Day One ends. Three silences settle back over the Waystone Inn.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000},{"id":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000093","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","number":93,"title":"Epilogue: A Silence of Three Parts","synopsis":"The epilogue silence — same inn, same man, same waiting. But the story has been started, and started things cannot be entirely unstarted.","notes":"","createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000}],"events":[{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"The Inn's Silence","description":"The Waystone Inn breathes with a deep, patient silence — the kind that fills a place when its owner has stopped fighting it. Kote polishes the bar and waits.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":0,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Scrael Encounter","description":"A scrael — one of the black, crab-like creatures spreading fear across the countryside — is found near the inn. Kote and Bast deal with it quickly, efficiently, and without the flair of a legend.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":1,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Tending the Inn","description":"An ordinary day at the Waystone. Kote serves cider, listens to the locals worry about the roads, and pretends he has nothing more pressing on his mind.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":2,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"The Smith's Prentice","description":"Jake Carter, the smith's prentice, arrives injured after a scrael attack. The gathering of frightened locals marks the creeping wrongness of the world outside the inn.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":3,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Saving Chronicler","description":"Chronicler — the famous scribe Devan Lochees — arrives half-dead on the road. Kote brings him in, and Bast's eyes sharpen with calculation.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":4,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Negotiations","description":"Chronicler makes his pitch: he wants to record the true story of Kvothe's life. Kvothe deflects, deflects, and then — unexpectedly — agrees.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":5,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"The Agreement","description":"Terms are struck. Three days. Three books. The truth. Kvothe pours two drinks and begins: \"I was a happy child.\"","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":6,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Early Life","description":"Kvothe describes his early life with the Edema Ruh — the fire and the road, music and stories, the shape of a childhood spent entirely in motion.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":7,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000008","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000008","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Meeting Ben","description":"Abenthy joins the troupe — a barrel-chested, oddly cheerful ex-arcanist. Young Kvothe is fascinated by the sympathy demonstration Ben gives, and pesters him mercilessly until Ben agrees to teach him.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":8,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000009","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000009","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Learning Sympathy","description":"Ben begins teaching Kvothe sympathy in earnest. The Alar — the mental split needed for binding — comes to Kvothe with startling ease. Ben is quietly alarmed by how fast his student learns.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":9,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000010","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000010","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Mastering Alar","description":"Kvothe masters the Alar: the ability to hold two opposing thoughts simultaneously without either weakening. Ben sets him harder and harder drills, and Kvothe clears them all.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":10,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Binding Iron","description":"Kvothe binds iron — his first real sympathy working. The heat flows from one piece of metal to another and he feels the sting of it in his own skin. He grins through the pain.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":11,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Gathering Info","description":"Kvothe digs through Ben's books, hungry for any scrap of information about the Chandrian. Ben answers his questions carefully, unwilling to encourage the obsession.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":12,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Frame Pause 1","description":"At the inn, Bast sets down his notes and stretches. Kvothe pauses his telling, refills the drinks, and both men rest in the quiet.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":13,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000014","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000014","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Binding the Air","description":"Ben teaches Kvothe to call the wind by name — just for a moment, just a breath. It is the first time Kvothe touches something older and stranger than sympathy. Ben is shaken afterward.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":14,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000015","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000015","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Ben Departs","description":"Ben decides to leave — he has found a woman and a town to settle in. The farewell is warm and sad. He tells Kvothe: go to the University, study hard, and stay away from the Chandrian.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":15,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000016","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000016","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Troupe Massacred","description":"Kvothe returns from gathering wood to find his entire troupe slaughtered. His parents lie among the dead. The fire still burns. He catches a glimpse of pale-haired Cinder before darkness takes him.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000010","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000020"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":16,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000017","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000017","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Frame Pause 2","description":"Back in the inn. Kvothe's voice is flat as he describes what he saw. The fire. The bodies. The silence that came after. Chronicler writes without comment.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":17,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000018","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000018","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Wandering","description":"Kvothe wanders the roads for weeks, barely eating, barely thinking. The troupe's routes mean nothing to him now. He moves because stopping feels like dying.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":18,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000019","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000019","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Bleeding Fingers","description":"Playing his lute by a roadside, Kvothe's fingers bleed from hours of playing. The music is the only thing that still makes sense. A merchant offers him a ride to Tarbean.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":["40000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":19,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000020","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000020","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Arriving in Tarbean","description":"The city swallows Kvothe whole. He is twelve, alone, and has nothing. Tarbean is massive, indifferent, and dangerous. He finds a ruin to sleep in and begins the long work of surviving.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":20,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000021","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000021","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Tarbean Survival","description":"Three years pass. Kvothe lives in the Tarbean slums — Waterside and the Dockside warren. He begs, steals, and slowly hollows out. He calls himself Kote and forgets, most days, who he used to be.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":21,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000022","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000022","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Midwinter","description":"Midwinter in Tarbean. Kvothe is arrested during a festival and thrown into a holding pen. The cold and the hunger are familiar; the humiliation is worse.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":22,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000023","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000023","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Skarpi's Tale","description":"Kvothe hears the storyteller Skarpi hold a crowd at a tavern — not with tricks, but with a history of Lanre that makes the old stories feel like lies. Kvothe listens until dawn.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":23,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000024","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000024","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Leaving Tarbean","description":"Something shifts. Kvothe starts remembering who he is. He retrieves his lute from where he hid it, mends it badly, and begins practising again. The city is no longer a trap — it is a place he is leaving.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":24,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000025","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000025","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Defending the Ruh","description":"On the road out of Tarbean, Kvothe defends a small Edema Ruh family from a group of soldiers who have no right to harass them. The old reflexes are back.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":25,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000026","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000026","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Skarpi Arrested","description":"Skarpi is arrested by a church official for what he told the crowd about Lanre. The official — calm, pitiless — seems to know exactly what Skarpi was doing and why it is forbidden.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":26,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000027","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000027","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Preparations","description":"Kvothe prepares himself — mentally, practically. He rehearses what he knows of sympathy. He works out what he will need to say to impress the masters. He plans.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":27,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000028","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000028","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Meeting Denna","description":"On the road near Anilin, Kvothe meets a young woman travelling alone — Denna. They share a fire and conversation and she is unlike anyone he has met. She leaves before morning.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000008","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["travel"],"sortOrder":28,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000029","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000029","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Traveling with Denna","description":"Kvothe continues along the Great Stone Road toward the University, unable to stop thinking about the girl on the road. He is equal parts excited and terrified about what lies ahead.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000009","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":29,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000030","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000030","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Arrival at University","description":"Kvothe arrives at the University and immediately feels underprepared and underdressed. The campus is larger than he imagined. Everything is more complicated. He tries not to show it.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":30,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000031","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Admissions","description":"The masters assess Kvothe in admissions — Elodin's questions are bewildering, Hemme's are hostile, Kilvin's are delighted. They set his tuition at three talents. He barely has that.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":31,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000032","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000032","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Adjusting","description":"Kvothe adjusts to University life — the schedule, the titles, the strange social rules. Simmon and Wilem become his first real friends.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":32,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000033","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000033","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Archives Visit","description":"Kvothe visits the Archives for the first time and is dazzled. So much knowledge. He immediately begins looking for anything about the Chandrian.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":33,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000034","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000034","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"First Classes","description":"Kvothe attends Hemme's sympathy class and manages — just barely — not to get himself expelled in the first session.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":34,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000035","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000035","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Meeting Ambrose","description":"Kvothe encounters Ambrose Jakis in the Archives and the dislike is mutual, instant, and complete. Ambrose is used to winning these encounters. Kvothe is not interested in losing.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000010"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["archives","rivalry"],"sortOrder":35,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000036","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000036","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Trouble in Archives","description":"Kvothe's bluntness and curiosity earn him a ban from the Archives. The loss is devastating — it was the one place he felt at home at the University.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":36,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000037","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000037","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"The Fishery","description":"Kvothe begins working in the Fishery under Kilvin, crafting sympathy devices. He is good at it immediately. The money helps. Kilvin's approval means more than he expected.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":37,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000038","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000038","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Sympathy Advancement","description":"Kvothe advances rapidly in his sympathy studies — his knowledge and his Alar are both far ahead of his year. He is simultaneously admired and resented.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":38,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000039","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000039","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Hemme's Class","description":"Hemme attempts to make an example of Kvothe in class by demonstrating how sympathy can cause pain. Kvothe redirects it back onto Hemme, in front of the entire group.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":39,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000040","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000040","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"On the Horns","description":"Kvothe is brought before the masters — \"On the Horns\" — on Hemme's complaint. Master Lorren and Master Kilvin speak in his favour. He is suspended for one term instead of expelled.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":40,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000041","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000041","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Talent Pipes","description":"Kvothe plays at the Eolian and earns his talent pipes despite a string breaking mid-performance. It is one of the finest things he has ever done.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":41,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000042","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000042","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Reconnecting with Denna","description":"Kvothe and Denna spend time in Imre — talking, playing, circling around what neither of them will say. She mentions her patron but says nothing useful about him.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":42,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000043","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000043","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Lute Destroyed","description":"Ambrose has Kvothe's lute destroyed — smashed beyond repair. It was his father's. It survived Tarbean. The loss tears something open in Kvothe that he had mostly managed to keep closed.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000010"],"involvedItemIds":["40000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"tags":["conflict","music"],"sortOrder":43,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000044","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000044","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Revenge on Ambrose","description":"Kvothe engineers a careful, legally deniable revenge on Ambrose involving a bone-tar fire and considerable embarrassment. It is not enough. It never will be.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000010"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":44,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000045","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000045","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Frame Pause 3","description":"An interlude. Bast pours more drinks. Kvothe stretches his hand — the one that shakes sometimes — and does not mention it.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":45,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000046","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000046","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Devi's Loan","description":"Kvothe goes to Devi in Imre and secures a loan at reasonable interest. The collateral is a phial of his blood. Both of them know what that means.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":46,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000047","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000047","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Schema Creation","description":"Kvothe creates the Bloodless — his Fishery masterwork — and earns the rank of Re'lar. He also uses some of the loan money to buy a new, finer lute.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":47,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000048","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000048","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"University Life","description":"A term of ordinary University life: classes, sympathy practice, work in the Fishery, evenings at Anker's with Sim and Wil.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":48,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000049","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000049","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"The Underthing","description":"Kvothe discovers the Underthing — a labyrinth of tunnels and forgotten passages beneath the University. He obtains a key from Puppet.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":49,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000050","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000050","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Meeting Puppet","description":"Kvothe follows the Underthing deeper and meets Puppet — an odd, otherworldly figure who tends a room full of Aturan artifacts and speaks in riddles. Elodin's name comes up.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":50,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000051","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000051","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Remembering Tarbean","description":"Kvothe rides past the part of Tarbean he once knew. He watches it from a distance and does not stop.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":51,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000052","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000052","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Trebon News","description":"A letter brings news: strange, violent deaths near Trebon, with signs of the Chandrian. Kvothe cannot sit still.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":52,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000053","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000053","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Journey to Trebon","description":"Kvothe and Simmon make the journey to Trebon — fast travel and nervous energy. Kvothe is thinking about Cinder. He doesn't say so.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":53,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000054","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000054","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Farm Investigation","description":"A farmstead near Trebon has been destroyed — the family killed, the signs unmistakable. Kvothe finds painted figures and a name scratched into the wood. His hands are steady. His stomach is not.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":54,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000055","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000055","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Finding Denna","description":"In the wreckage of a travelling troupe, Kvothe finds Denna — alive, barely, in the ruins. She has been drugged with Denner resin.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":55,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000056","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000056","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Draccus Encounter","description":"Kvothe pieces together what happened: a draccus has been drawn to the area and is eating Denner resin from the hidden drug operation. The Chandrian were here first. Now there is a very large, very drugged lizard to deal with.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":56,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000057","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000057","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Tracking Draccus","description":"Kvothe tracks the draccus toward Trebon — a creature the size of a barn, moving with the terrifying certainty of something that has never had a predator.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":57,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000058","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000058","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Denna Drugged","description":"Denna regains consciousness. She has been drugged for days. She does not remember much. She is furious about it, and frightened.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":58,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000059","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000059","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Saving Trebon","description":"Kvothe leads the draccus away from Trebon using fire and sympathy — a desperate improvisation that burns through his body heat and leaves him shaking.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":59,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000060","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000060","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Draccus Attack","description":"The draccus attacks the village anyway. Kvothe has to get ahead of it, stay ahead of it, and keep improvising.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":60,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000061","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000061","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Slaying the Beast","description":"Kvothe kills the draccus by using sympathy to detonate a bell tower onto its head. The explosion leaves him half-dead on the ground. He considers this a victory.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":61,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000062","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000062","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Recovery","description":"Kvothe recovers — slowly. Denna has vanished again by the time he can walk. He is given forty talents by the grateful mayor and feels hollow anyway.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":62,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000063","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000063","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Return to Imre","description":"Kvothe returns to Imre, exhausted and filthy and richer than he has ever been. None of it feels like enough.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":63,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000064","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000064","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Financial Ruin","description":"The forty talents do not last. Tuition, Devi's interest, new strings, food. University life has a way of consuming money absolutely.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":64,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000065","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000065","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Continuing Studies","description":"A new term. Kvothe studies, works, schemes for coin, and tries to get back into the Archives via any legal means available.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":65,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000066","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000066","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Fishery Fire","description":"A fire breaks out in the Fishery. Kvothe pulls Fela out of the burning room before she dies. He is badly burned. Kilvin's praise afterward embarrasses him.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":66,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000067","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000067","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Saving Fela","description":"Fela thanks Kvothe. The University community notices. Ambrose is irritated. Kvothe is just glad his hands still work.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":67,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000068","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000068","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Elodin's Student","description":"Kvothe corners Elodin — again — and this time Elodin actually agrees to teach him. He sets Kvothe an assignment that makes no obvious sense.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":68,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000069","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000069","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Time with Denna","description":"Kvothe and Denna spend a long afternoon in Imre — music and talk and the frustrating closeness that never quite becomes anything else.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":69,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000070","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000070","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"More Sympathy","description":"Kvothe works on his sympathy. His Alar is now strong enough that maintaining multiple simultaneous bindings barely costs him effort.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":70,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000071","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000071","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Creating a Gram","description":"Kvothe creates the gram — a small iron disk inscribed with protective sympathy bindings — in the Fishery. Kilvin watches with interest. It works.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":71,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000072","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000072","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Ambrose Plots","description":"Ambrose is plotting something more serious than embarrassment. He uses his family's connections. Kvothe starts watching his back.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000010"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":72,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000073","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000073","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Paying Tuition","description":"Tuition time again. Kvothe scrapes together the money through a combination of Fishery work, busking, and careful pride-management.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":73,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000074","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000074","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Rumors","description":"Rumours spread around the University about Kvothe's various exploits. Some are accurate. Most are not. All of them are more flattering than he deserves.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":74,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000075","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000075","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Frame Pause 4","description":"Another pause at the inn. Bast refills the fire. Kvothe's hands wrap around his cup like they are holding something in.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":75,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000076","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000076","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Devi Dealings","description":"Back to Devi's. More negotiations. Kvothe has never been entirely comfortable here — she is too sharp, and he knows she knows it.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":76,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000077","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000077","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Tricking Forward","description":"Kvothe pulls off something clever against one of Ambrose's schemes. He is pleased with himself for exactly as long as it takes Ambrose to think of the next move.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":77,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000078","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000078","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Master Ash","description":"Denna is being taught by a patron called Master Ash who, Kvothe increasingly suspects, is not just eccentric but dangerous. He cannot prove it. She does not want his suspicions.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":78,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000079","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000079","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Archives Search","description":"Kvothe searches the Archives — legally this time, with grudging permission — for anything about the Amyr, the Chandrian, or the ancient wars. He finds fragments. Only fragments.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":79,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000080","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000080","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Day Passes","description":"An ordinary day. Lectures, Fishery work, an evening with Sim and Wil. Kvothe almost forgets, for a few hours, that he is supposed to be looking for something.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":80,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000081","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000081","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Arrogance","description":"Kvothe is reprimanded for arrogance during a practical session. He deserved it. He argues back anyway.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":81,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000082","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000082","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Studying Naming","description":"Elodin's Naming lessons continue. Today he tells Kvothe to go listen to the wind for three hours. Kvothe does it. Something at the edge of his mind shifts.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":82,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000083","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000083","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Considering Future","description":"Kvothe considers the future: the University, the Chandrian, Denna, the name of the wind. They circle each other in his mind without resolving.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":83,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000084","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000084","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Trouble in Imre","description":"An argument in Imre with Denna about Master Ash becomes something uglier than either of them wanted. She leaves. He stays. Neither of them said the right thing.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":84,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000085","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000085","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Frame Pause 5","description":"Chronicler puts down his stylus. Kvothe is quiet for a moment — longer than usual. Bast does not look at either of them.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":85,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000086","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000086","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Naming the Wind","description":"Riding back to the University in a thunderstorm, something opens in Kvothe. He calls the name of the wind — properly, completely — and the storm responds. He does not fully understand what he has done. He knows it was real.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000012","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner","magic"],"sortOrder":86,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000087","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000087","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Reflections","description":"Back at the University, Kvothe sits with it. To know the name of a thing is to see it differently forever. He is still working out what that means.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000011","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":87,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000088","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000088","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Frame Pause 6","description":"Evening at the inn. Kvothe asks Chronicler if he is still writing. Chronicler looks at his hands. Yes. Still writing.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":88,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000089","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000089","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Story Continues","description":"Back in the story, near its end for the day. Kvothe ties up the last threads of this particular telling and looks out the window.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":89,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000090","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000090","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Preparing to Finish Day 1","description":"The candles are burning low. Kvothe wraps the last parts of the day's account with the care of a man who has been doing this all his life.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":90,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000091","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000091","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","title":"Wrapping Up","description":"The first day of telling ends. Three books worth of story. Three days total. Kvothe goes quiet and pours one last drink.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000013","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["inner"],"sortOrder":91,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000092","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000092","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"First Day Ends","description":"A silence of three parts fills the inn again. Kvothe sets down his cup. Outside, the road is empty. Tomorrow there will be more.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":92,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false},{"id":"70000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000093","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","chapterId":"60000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000093","timelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","title":"Epilogue","description":"The same silence as the prologue — but different. Heavier. Something has shifted in the inn, in Kvothe, perhaps in the world.","locationMarkerId":"a0000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007","involvedCharacterIds":["30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"],"involvedItemIds":[],"tags":["frame"],"sortOrder":93,"travelDays":null,"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000,"isFlashback":false}],"blobs":[],"travelModes":[],"timelineRelationships":[{"id":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003","worldId":"10000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000","sourceTimelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001","targetTimelineId":"20000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000002","type":"frame_narrative","label":"Kvothe narrates his life to Chronicler","description":"Kvothe tells his autobiography over three days at the Waystone Inn.","anchors":[{"kind":"character","entityId":"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000001"}],"syncPoints":[],"createdAt":1713200000000,"updatedAt":1713200000000}],"crossTimelineArtifacts":[],"relationshipPositions":{"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000007":{"x":548.3315563198624,"y":152.11177987962168},"b1e30133-29d0-4f94-8f70-e33df9d9f312":{"x":675.2505588993981,"y":176.30232158211524},"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000020":{"x":-174.4110060189166,"y":273.1965606190886},"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000005":{"x":181.08478073946688,"y":577.3228929257579},"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000008":{"x":443.6811693895099,"y":539.4245915735168},"d3763704-c74f-431b-9045-8e415d8029d0":{"x":-246.11246775580398,"y":471.453826311264},"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000003":{"x":-106.75391229578676,"y":138.96474634565777},"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000006":{"x":65.73516766981943,"y":61.00223559759243},"30000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000019":{"x":247.3458297506449,"y":100.04952708512468}},"suppressedIssueIds":[]}